title: BBC.Forces.of.Nature.with.Brian.Cox.Complete.Series.720p.x264
description:
Professor Brian Cox combines some of the most spectacular sights on Earth with our deepest understanding of the universe to reveal how the planet's beauty is created by just a handful of forces.

Episode 1: Professor Brian Cox investigates the stunning diversity of shapes in the natural world.

Episode 2: Professor Brian Cox follows the Earth's epic journey though space.

Episode 3: Professor Brian Cox investigates the ingredients which are the building blocks of life.

Episode 4: Professor Brian Cox explains the science behind the colours of the planet.
